Subject: [PATCH 0354/1532] DPI: Added new DTS files to run regex demos as
 Linux applications

Two DTS files (one for XLP2XX and the other for XLP3XX) are added which are to be used when running the regex demos as Linux applications
Updated the build-dtb.sh script to compile the new DTS files into respective .dtb files
[Based on SDK 3.2]
Signed-off-by: Quanyang Wang <quanyang.wang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp2xx-linux-dpi.dts | 126 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux-dpi.dts | 129 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 255 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp2xx-linux-dpi.dts
 create mode 100644 arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp3xx-linux-dpi.dts

diff --git a/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp2xx-linux-dpi.dts b/arch/mips/boot/dts/xlp2xx-linux-dpi.dts
new file mode 100644
